    public class GetNavData
extends NavTagHelper
    Custom tag to get NavData into request. 'id' is mandatory (request attribute name where the NavData are stored) 'url' is optional (if not defined current url in RequestUrl is looked for) Version 1.1 (2018-01-15)
    Author:
    Fugerit
